.SH RETURN VALUES
.sp
.LP
Routines that return pointers always return
.I NULL
on error. Routines
that return an integer return one of the following:
.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B E_OK
.ad
.RS 21n
.rt
The routine returned successfully.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B E_SYSTEM_ERROR
.ad
.RS 21n
.rt
System error.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B E_BAD_ARGUMENT
.ad
.RS 21n
.rt
An incorrect argument was passed to the routine.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B E_POSTED
.ad
.RS 21n
.rt
The menu is already posted.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B E_CONNECTED
.ad
.RS 21n
.rt
One or more items are already connected to another menu.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B E_BAD_STATE
.ad
.RS 21n
.rt
The routine was called from an initialization or termination function.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B E_NO_ROOM
.ad
.RS 21n
.rt
The menu does not fit within its subwindow.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B E_NOT_POSTED
.ad
.RS 21n
.rt
The menu has not been posted.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B E_UNKNOWN_COMMAND
.ad
.RS 21n
.rt
An unknown request was passed to the menu driver.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B E_NO_MATCH
.ad
.RS 21n
.rt
The character failed to match.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B E_NOT_SELECTABLE
.ad
.RS 21n
.rt
The item cannot be selected.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B E_NOT_CONNECTED
.ad
.RS 21n
.rt
No items are connected to the menu.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
.B E_REQUEST_DENIED
.ad
.RS 21n
.rt
The menu driver could not process the request.
.RE

